Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.79,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我内心的黑暗面是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,过去无法抹去的哀伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.59,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 内心亦无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}放飞Blastar 伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:22.27,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}无法避开的道路 何时起变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:26.98,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,400)}谁都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:29.52,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命运什么的谁管它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,无法忍受 cry for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.65,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,ah ah ah alone in my world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:36.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}响彻着的爱之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.32,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,歪曲的现实 弯曲的愿望
